videos.description: Brian Herrien powers his way across the goal line from three yards out to give Georgia an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Herrien plows ahead for Georgia TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herrien plows ahead for Georgia TD

videos.description: Jake Fromm delivers a short pass to Dominick Blaylock, who outruns the Arkansas State defense for a 60-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blaylock sprints up the sideline for 60-yard TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blaylock sprints up the sideline for 60-yard TD

videos.description: Jake Fromm dumps a pass off to D'Andre Swift, who takes it all the way to the end zone and extends Georgia's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Swift slices through the defense for 48-yard TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Swift slices through the defense for 48-yard TD

videos.description: Georgia fans pack the stands wearing pink to show their support and honor Arkansas State coach Blake Anderson's wife, Wendy, who died Aug. 19 after a two-year battle with breast cancer.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Georgia ‘pink out’ honors wife of Arkansas St. coach) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia 'pink out' honors wife of Arkansas St. coach

videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Lawrence Cager for a 5-yard touchdown and puts Georgia ahead 34-0 before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm throws 3rd TD pass in the 1st half) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm throws 3rd TD pass in the 1st half

videos.description: James Cook runs around the outside for a 37-yard touchdown and pads Georgia's commanding lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's Cook goes untouched for the TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's Cook goes untouched for the TD

videos.description: Georgia RB Zamir White caps off an 83-yard drive with a short touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (White runs in another Georgia TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: White runs in another Georgia TD

videos.description: George Pickens makes a great catch on the sideline and gets both feet down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pickens makes terrific toe-tap grab) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pickens makes terrific toe-tap grab

videos.description: Kenny McIntosh bounces to the outside and shows off his speed for a 62-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McIntosh's 62-yard TD puts Georgia up 55-0) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: McIntosh's 62-yard TD puts Georgia up 55-0
